  "text": [
    "<strong dir=\"rtl\">חָצִיף</strong>, <strong dir=\"rtl\">חֲצִיפָא</strong> m.  (<a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_חֲצַף.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, חֲצַף 1\">חֲצַף</a>, sub. <span dir=\"rtl\">אַפִּין</span>)  <b>1)</b> <i>bare-faced, impudent, impertinent</i>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Aramaic_Targum_to_Psalms.17.4\" data-ref=\"Aramaic Targum to Psalms 17:4\">Targ. Ps. XVII, 4</a>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Aramaic_Targum_to_Ecclesiastes.8.1\" data-ref=\"Aramaic Targum to Ecclesiastes 8:1\">Targ. Koh. VIII, 1</a> <span dir=\"rtl\">חֲצִיף אפין</span> (constr.); a. e.—<a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Berakhot.34b.31\" data-ref=\"Berakhot 34b:31\">Ber. 34ᵇ</a>; <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Sotah.7b.12\" data-ref=\"Sotah 7b:12\">Sot. 7ᵇ</a> ח׳ עלי מאן וכ׳ I consider him impertinent who &c. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Kiddushin.33a.16\" data-ref=\"Kiddushin 33a:16\">Kidd. 33ᵃ</a> <span dir=\"rtl\">כמה ח׳ האי גברא</span> how irreverently behaves this man; a. e.—<i>Fem.</i> <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_חָצִיף.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, חָצִיף 1\">חֲצִיפָא</a>, <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_חֲרִיפְתָּא.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, חֲרִיפְתָּא 1\">חֲצִיפְתָּא</a>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Moed_Katan.16b.13\" data-ref=\"Moed Katan 16b:13\">M. Kat. 16ᵇ</a>. Y. Taan. III, 66ᵈ top.—Pl. m. <span dir=\"rtl\">חֲצִיפִין</span>, constr. <span dir=\"rtl\">חֲצִיפֵי</span>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Targum_Jonathan_on_Exodus.28.37\" data-ref=\"Targum Jonathan on Exodus 28:37\">Targ. Y. Ex. XXVIII, 37</a>; a. e. <b>—2)</b> <i>undaunted, persevering, strong</i>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Yalkut_Shimoni_on_Nach.989.8\" data-ref=\"Yalkut Shimoni on Nach 989:8\">Yalk. Koh. 989</a>, v. <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_נָטוֹרָא.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, נָטוֹרָא 1\">נָטוֹרָא</a>. Pesik. Shub., p. 161ᵃ <span dir=\"rtl\">ח׳ נצח לבישא וכ׳</span> the persevering (in prayer) conquers even the bad man, so much the more the Good One of the world; Y. Taan. II, 65ᵇ <span dir=\"rtl\">חֲצִיפָח … לכשירא</span> (corr. acc.); <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Yalkut_Shimoni_on_Nach.550.6\" data-ref=\"Yalkut Shimoni on Nach 550:6\">Yalk. Jon. 550</a>."
  ],
